{"tid":2296504,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲有人玩7500","createTime":"2020-11-22T13:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T01:15:20.000Z","uid":49342,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b3dea3cff41f28ecdb2878673681234b39db14df","tid":2296504,"uid":49342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:53:36.000Z","msg":"年頭1月17日Hsi升上29000, 7500跌到5.9<br />\n依家Hsi只係26400, 但7500得返5.5，仲低過恆指最高位嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3月入咗7500 strong hold緊的巴打出黎講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2555a685d0048ba5ba8b55680debdbb06b5ace","tid":2296504,"uid":37389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"玩7500同SH 7500 兩樣嘢嚟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6fccdae6e268442ffcf1d04027f90a116edd596","tid":2296504,"uid":34060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> SH 7500 真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"a43199f276f0201a974836c5a32ad65e8358193f","tid":2296504,"uid":49342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af2555a685d0048ba5ba8b55680debdbb06b5ace","tid":2296504,"uid":37389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"玩7500同SH 7500 兩樣嘢嚟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"或者你啱，但唔SH駛乜買7500？<br />\n直接入熊算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e67cbb3ee7ee0c0be879ad4d54ec506f4a241d1","tid":2296504,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6dc7e1e86f3bb1ecb3d5da2518c0dbcc27f5c8a","tid":2296504,"uid":259010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:02:23.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">反向ETF 都是以期貨來複製大市反向倍數表現，即是以期指淡倉來建倉，槓反產品的發行商每日均會調整投資組合，確保產品提供單日固定的槓桿比率。<br />\n<br />\n因此，當持有反向ETF產品超過1日，投資回報有很大機會偏離相關指數累計表現。<br />\n<br />\n偏離不一定等於跑輸，反向ETF因為每日調整投資組合，都會出現複合效應，當大市連日大跌，有明顯單向走勢，令單向走勢更為明顯。理論上，在此情景下，投資者長揸槓桿反向ETF會跑贏指數的兩倍表現。<br />\n<br />\n相反，當大市變得日升日跌的上落市格局，因為不同交易日倉位互相蠶食表現，不論正向或反向的槓桿ETF表現都會遜於相關指數累計回報兩倍的表現。</span>"},{"pid":"b30a71b88a68e00c56a2a3d4e19124164c65436f","tid":2296504,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:02:54.000Z","msg":"你問個莊lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b3e5d173e71a7101fada975f31548fb767e922","tid":2296504,"uid":198241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"直接SHORT SELL 細期仲抵玩啦<br />\n7500 比窮人玩"},{"pid":"b7c7249296cb7f6f813e094cbcc5a45ddf2119cd","tid":2296504,"uid":111316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:18:41.000Z","msg":"咁7200長揸玩唔玩得過？睇落好似都跟到價"},{"pid":"cb198bf78922d05ac6d60043a515e3917892b8bc","tid":2296504,"uid":178485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"如果3月SH 7500到而家會唔心理變態 <br />\n日日都希望個市跌 但跌唔到仲要升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f20a5a9faebf81be261573105c822fc1da66f0b","tid":2296504,"uid":49342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7c7249296cb7f6f813e094cbcc5a45ddf2119cd","tid":2296504,"uid":111316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:18:41.000Z","msg":"咁7200長揸玩唔玩得過？睇落好似都跟到價"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:44:31.000Z","msg":"上市日？：2017年3月17日 Hsi 24309, 7200 7.5<br />\n近期類似指數價位：2020年10月16日 Hsi 24386, 7200 7.5<br />\n如果咁計的話起碼唔會大蝕，不過記得有位ching驗證過其實hold 7500同hold 2800差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1eb573dbef3a36eb0a7f2efb3cb60960c5eac49","tid":2296504,"uid":49342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f20a5a9faebf81be261573105c822fc1da6